<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      background-color: #e53e3e;
      color: white;
    }
    .content {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f7fafc;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #0a2540;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      color: #718096;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Payment Failed for Order #{{orderNumber}}</h2>
      <p>We're sorry, but we were unable to process your payment for the order placed on {{orderDate}}.</p>
      
      <h3>What happened?</h3>
      <p>Your payment was declined. This could be due to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Insufficient funds</li>
        <li>Incorrect card details</li>
        <li>Card expired or blocked</li>
        <li>Bank security measures</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>What to do next?</h3>
      <p>You can try the following:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Check your card details</li>
        <li>Ensure you have sufficient funds</li>
        <li>Try a different payment method</li>
        <li>Contact your bank if the issue persists</li>
      </ul>

      <a href="http://localhost:3000/checkout" class="button">
        Try Payment Again
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Need help? Contact our support team.</p>
      <p>SneakerAlot Customer Support</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 